-# About
%section.m-about
  .l-constrained
    %h1 Smart, Simple & Effective
    .about-overview
      %p You want a website that communicates with your audience and gets results. One page sites offer your visitors a chance to quickly access information in a well organized experience. Instead of navigating through numerous pages, visitors to your site will be able to find exactly what they are looking for and make an informed decision. Plus, the single page format allows for a creative presentation that will look great on all modern devices.

-# Features
%section.m-features
  .l-constrained
    .features-tagline
      %h5 Websites designed to get your product, service, location or event noticed.
    .features-display
      = image_tag "responsive-display.png"
      %small= link_to "AIGA Dish Conference 2013", "http://www.lacroixdesign.net/portfolio/dish-2013", target: "_blank"
  .l-constrained
    .features-item
      %h2 Get Online Quickly
      %p In today's competitive market, your website is a crucial channel for reaching your audience. Through our design process, we will work with you to get a fantastic website online quickly.
    .features-item
      %h2 Custom Design
      %p Your business is unique so your website should be as well. Each site will be designed specifically for your brand and content. You won't be receiving a template, it will be a brand new site.
    .features-item
      %h2 Great On Every Device
      %p Your site will look great on any size screen. Using responsive web design, we will create a website that responds and adapts to the browser size to create a great experience on every device. 


-# Details
%section.m-details
  .l-constrained
    .details-rules
      %h1 What You Will Receive
      %ul
        %li In three weeks, you will have an eye catching site with static content designed to market your product, service, location or event. 
        %li Your site will be an original design created to best represent your brand and deliver your content to your audience.
        %li The new site will be responsive, meaning that it will respond and adapt to the size of the browser making sure that your content looks as great on a phone or tablet as it does on a desktop or laptop.
        %li The opportunity to work with an experienced design studio created to help businesses grow. 
        %li Once the site is launched, we will provide up to one hour of time for any minor edits to the content on your site. 
    .details-rules
      %h1 What You Won't Receive
      %ul
        %li Copywriting, custom photography and branding elements are not included. However, we do offer these services and would love to partner with you to create them but it will affect cost and timeline.
        %li Site will be composed of static content and therefore, there will not be a content management system. If you would require on, we are well versed in creating these solutions. We could quote out this project for you if needed. 
        %li Hosting is not included. We offer very affordable hosting packages or, we can recommend a solution for you and handle the installation of the site. 
        %li Domain Registration is not included. Therefore, you will need to register yours with the registry of your choice or we could recommend one. 
                

